{"tid":2407700,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新年祝願觀眾身體健康　姜濤：身體係革命嘅本錢","createTime":"2021-02-14T09:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T10:00:26.000Z","uid":212249,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"273adc2489ba592e6374ed50ec8ab89e40bced60","tid":2407700,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T09:04:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20210214-27_1LBRI_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20210214-27_1LBRI_1200x0.png&h=7f0f8af3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2019 年 9 月反送中運動期間，姜濤在銅鑼灣遭防暴警察截查，相片在網上瘋傳，網民亦創作了一句「沒有暴徒，只有姜濤」的口號。他近日出席一個網上節目時向觀眾拜年，祝願大家身體健康，「身體係革命嘅本錢，所以希望大家身體健康！」<br />\n<br />\n姜濤在年三十晚（11 日）出席陳志雲的網上節目《Stephen．傾》，被問到會怎樣向粉絲觀眾拜年：<br />\n<br />\n我都唔係識好多成語，希望新嘅一年祝大家身體健康。雖然好老土，但我親身經歷，覺得身體健康係一件非常重要嘅事情。身體係革命嘅本錢，所以希望大家身體健康！<br />\n<br />\n黑打扮兼戴上黑口罩現身銅鑼灣，被防暴警截查及搜袋。其經理人「花姐」事後解釋姜濤一向都是穿黑衣示人。姜濤事後於IG報平安「我沒事，請大家放心。」<br />\n<br />\n去年 3 月，姜濤被指在 IG 讚好一則藍絲留言「廢青仔，快啲移民英國，英國首相叫你哋生死自理啦。」事後他承認責任，並解釋是因為手指太肥撳錯掣。"},{"pid":"656f1b114eee71fe1e778f4d971c7cd976aae4dd","tid":2407700,"uid":212249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T09:04:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/新年祝願觀眾身體健康-姜濤-身體係革命嘅本錢/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B4%E7%A5%9D%E9%A1%98%E8%A7%80%E7%9C%BE%E8%BA%AB%E9%AB%94%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7-%E5%A7%9C%E6%BF%A4-%E8%BA%AB%E9%AB%94%E4%BF%82%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD%E5%98%85%E6%9C%AC%E9%8C%A2%2F&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLuW6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=aa853755\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B4%E7%A5%9D%E9%A1%98%E8%A7%80%E7%9C%BE%E8%BA%AB%E9%AB%94%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7-%E5%A7%9C%E6%BF%A4-%E8%BA%AB%E9%AB%94%E4%BF%82%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD%E5%98%85%E6%9C%AC%E9%8C%A2%2F&h=a8fea8e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/新年祝願觀眾身體健康-姜濤-身體係革命嘅本錢/</a>"},{"pid":"b46d647dd48122f2dbb153f05f256543eed655d3","tid":2407700,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T09:58:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2460000/2462415/keungso_thumb_20190929_D_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2460000%2F2462415%2Fkeungso_thumb_20190929_D_1024.jpg&h=f0337d1d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0140229a8d206fe0c7b1c316f9a8d4cad55f98f","tid":2407700,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T10:00:26.000Z","msg":"變革香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}